description:
Guy's Grocery Games - Season 14, Episode 7




Superstars Tournament Part 3

In the third leg of the Guy's Grocery Games: Superstars Tournament, the remaining six chefs are all given the same grocery list, but must compete in three one-on-one battles. The winners of these match-ups are safe, but the three that get edged out head into the Redemption Round. Which two chefs will rejoin their peers for the semifinals and get another shot at becoming champions for charity?




Original Air Date: 03-Sep-2017
